l also enjoy reliable integration with current and future WooCommerce releases.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://woocommerce.com/products/pharmacy/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=storefrontaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;39.00";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:7:"ToyShop";s:5:"image";s:68:"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/toyshop.jpg?w=980";s:7:"excerpt";s:548:"<p style="margin-bottom: 1.618em;">Add some fun to your store with ToyShop. The engaging and colorful design of ToyShop makes it a perfect child theme or any store that sells exciting products that are aimed at customers that like to have fun. The outdoorsy style would even be perfect for a flower shop.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.618em;">Be sure to check out both demos:</p>\r\n<a class="button" href="http://demo2.woothemes.com/toyshop/">Children\'s Fashion</a> <a class="button" href="http://demo2.woothemes.com/garys-garden/">Flower Shop</a>";s:4:"link";s:108:"https://woocommerce.com/products/toyshop/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=storefrontaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;39.00";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:6:"Outlet";s:5:"image";s:67:"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/outlet.jpg?w=980";s:7:"excerpt";s:221:"Overclock your tech store with Outlet! Whether you sell boutique iPad jewellery or the nuts and bolts of hardware itself, Outlet will give your shop a stylish look and feel while enjoying the stability of Storefront core.";s:4:"link";s:107:"https://woocommerce.com/products/outlet/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=storefrontaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;39.00";}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:7:"ProShop";s:5:"image";s:68:"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/proshop.jpg?w=980";s:7:"excerpt";s:181:"Unlock the true potential of your sports clothing and equipment store with ProShop! It&#039;s metropolitan design provides an active aesthetic giving your store oodles of character.";s:4:"link";